[{"phelps":"AB00044PRO","text":"## WADIDI U'URAEWA\n* Teaching\nMaman! Ge om gega da uon!  Ge Ayop wande iram!  Iyan ma Ge kwiman ita dun gegawa. Dom pasukat tamo amba aneya gega amena den mu wat nagat mum, ap gapan mu Ge ita anan gega apane venasep piup ma uruga Ge aton gega gan amba nop wait gega wat senamep. Maman Ge mu den pasukat mugawa amba garagat gapan, sunup gapan, at bumak gapan, oma pose gapan, pon gapan, dawara gapan, Ge gindak mum, ap gapan mu Ge amun sitatao gega menan ao waiyamun amba gaup amun gega gapan.  Ipiri Ge gegenat Amun, Ap amba Aro aigap iren, amba Ge gegenat amat, Anuiyanawa  amba yavianawa.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"ecb6a166-fb6a-4755-b1c3-04772a458415","translations":[{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"}]},{"phelps":"AB00065STE","text":"## DAIYO MANIMANI U'URAEWA\n* Travel\nNe mumaget ao yon waingen Ge aeamat gega gapan.  Mamanawa!  Amba at pa nega aeveyan anusumat nega uruga Ge inagap, amba ne inat yonat nega Ge ae amat kwayup gega gwanap.  Amena kwiman gapan dom bain gega kakaewa wasuen nen, amba amat tanege siya pa nega tauwap, den siga ne Ge gogon gega gapan amat tanege imuna Ge gegenat anu sumat kaimaket inagap anu dawagep.  Maman da siga uon go Ge gegenataet di, Ge daiton, Ge om gega da uon, Uruga anuianawa, Uruga amat taianawa.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"d5606adb-16dd-4c30-948e-1d912b953aad","translations":[{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mt","lang_name":"Maltese"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"}]},{"phelps":"BB00148","text":"## EWAT VIRIP TAPEN U’URAEWA\n(The Fast\n\n \nWat taragat iragi kwiman Ayop ge inagap.  Iwa Ge wam sisip ma potap ganat wat magatam baran.  Ap menan den nop gega ase wat aroga baran menan amba da ne den wat ago tanek.\n\nWat taragat irani kwiman Ayop ge inagap.  Ne ao bariangin Ge inagap aroe gan sisip iniram toentane ganat venasen Dima opata yaunewa ge ibari ap gapan amnata yonana amba ise magatam tan amba den ase wat arogamean.  Ap menan oyama wasuena vise ne aiganap amba mu aigamup den waenapan ansena tobot taton negin daiton anitoniwa nagirewa.  Ao yone nu ago nune ainagat nimanep magunu mine venasep ao kwiman pae pose dune ganase potap unun anet.  Ap mepe nu bigip madoga nuga iragi ise bigiwaranep, baigan yaunewa tamanam nun.  Ne Ayop negawa! Ne orup ap di nonup baigan gega taniwa ginap watnatan amba Ge bagusisi ge aton gega den inamup.  Maman Ge dimat tamanam tane amba den ne imuna potana wareni nagire dere piup ma kakaewa megawa amba piup namunupe tau wepi den.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"15c2889b-029f-4777-af33-f3ad21e69c41","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"}]},{"phelps":"BB00623","text":"## RAUSIM OL TRABEL\n\nGod Yet i ken rausim ol trabel.  I gat arapela samting i ken mekim dispela wok?  Tok olsem: Litimapim nem bilong God.  Em Yet I God. Olgeta manmeri i wokman bilong En na olgeta i bihainim tok bilong En.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"90948408-34e4-41b3-83e0-750ee36f0b2f","translations":[{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"sne","lang_name":"Bau Bidayuh"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bla","lang_name":"Blackfoot"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"km","lang_name":"Central Khmer"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"chn","lang_name":"Chinook Jargon"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"cs","lang_name":"Czech"},{"language":"dgz","lang_name":"Daga"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fo","lang_name":"Faroese"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"gu","lang_name":"Gujarati"},{"language":"ha","lang_name":"Hausa"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"Hindi"},{"language":"ho","lang_name":"Hiri Motu"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"ik","lang_name":"Inupiaq"},{"language":"ga","lang_name":"Irish"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"ksd","lang_name":"Kuanua"},{"language":"kgf","lang_name":"Kube"},{"language":"dih","lang_name":"Kumiai"},{"language":"lkt","lang_name":"Lakota"},{"language":"lo","lang_name":"Lao"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mi","lang_name":"Maori"},{"language":"mr","lang_name":"Marathi"},{"language":"mh","lang_name":"Marshallese"},{"language":"moh","lang_name":"Mohawk"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"cnr","lang_name":"Montenegrin"},{"language":"meu","lang_name":"Motu"},{"language":"nal","lang_name":"Nalik"},{"language":"nv","lang_name":"Navajo"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"one","lang_name":"Oneida"},{"language":"pap","lang_name":"Papiamento"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"se","lang_name":"Sami"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"sl","lang_name":"Slovenian"},{"language":"st","lang_name":"Southern Sotho"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"wam","lang_name":"Wampanoag"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH00053MAG","text":"## AYOP WAT TARAGASEPEN U'URAEWA\n* Praise\nWat aimagam irani Maman Ge inagap.  Iwa Ge dun ganat, koa mentarin, Ge yaibobot sunanon, nonup baigan, ge uwae yamanok, Ge gawo bonabon, ge amun ge koa kapisi ibariwa.  Maman Ge gegenat anut gega gapan ra menan anuianawa, asik gega toentane Puiman Kanama anegawa mine en wana onep.  Den siga da apan imuga wareniwa. Ge amun gega wana Yauga Namu irena ge yaibobot paua mega ire yavep.  Irani amena kwiman gapan ge mapa piupa, da Ge om gega mine uon nagaet.  Ge Ayop wande iram, Ge piup kwiman eve use ine bukwa darat wani dawap waran mum ge waup aeamat taianawa ge yavianawa.  Ayop da den sia uon.  Ge gegenataet di Ge dun epara, aro amun, anut ge asik iragi ibariwa.  Wat ganatam O Maman! nao gega nagire gine namup.  Mu den yawagep, den imuberi bigi wara Mu toentane imaetararin nambae gan dotauvep.  Apa amba Ge iraga yave kakayasep, iwa Ge gek ingane matauan dima opata gega magatam taiagi amba Ge dun ganat gega veraut en tomagen.  Ipiri Ge irani piup ge kwiman Ayopewa dawap.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"5c4faaef-b5b8-4af8-aedb-bc7f923e6692","translations":[{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"sl","lang_name":"Slovenian"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH00074BLE","text":"## KOLIM NEM BILONG GOD\n\n\nBlesing i stap long olgeta liklik hap, na haus, na ples, na biktaun, na bel bilong ol man, na maunten, na ples hait, na hol, na ples daun, na graun, na solwara, na ailan, na ples kunai, we ol man i bin kolim nem bilong God na ol i bin amamas long En.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"a72d208b-f23e-4871-9c95-99edaff2c005","translations":[{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bla","lang_name":"Blackfoot"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"km","lang_name":"Central Khmer"},{"language":"chr","lang_name":"Cherokee"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"dgz","lang_name":"Daga"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"gwi","lang_name":"Gwich'in"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"hur","lang_name":"Halkomelem"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"ik","lang_name":"Inupiaq"},{"language":"ga","lang_name":"Irish"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"ksd","lang_name":"Kuanua"},{"language":"kgf","lang_name":"Kube"},{"language":"lkt","lang_name":"Lakota"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"lut","lang_name":"Lushootseed"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"med","lang_name":"Melpa"},{"language":"moh","lang_name":"Mohawk"},{"language":"meu","lang_name":"Motu"},{"language":"nv","lang_name":"Navajo"},{"language":"ttm","lang_name":"Northern Tutchone"},{"language":"oj","lang_name":"Ojibwe"},{"language":"one","lang_name":"Oneida"},{"language":"pap","lang_name":"Papiamento"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"se","lang_name":"Sami"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"shh","lang_name":"Shoshoni"},{"language":"slh","lang_name":"Sliammon"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH00154FIR","text":"## EWAT VIRIP TAPEN  U’URAEWA\n* The Fast\n\n* Ewat virip tapen siragam `Alá (Aigap) wam derewa (2) gapan aepi wam apane daiton (20) gapan uon tata.  Yaumak ap gapan ewat go kaum da marek eya dotauvepi gapan nata aepi wam geyarepi pauwa.  Yaumak ma guwanu aro wanapen, ao wasupen wamewa.  Orup en muga (15) gauwarap virip eya tain, waen bagurenawa, orup am nainiwa vek denawa, amba waenapan tanewa den.\n\nNe esuna ewat mega virip taiyangin taba ge kaum den virip taiyangin.  Ap menan bumagana bigi wat, wat aimagam ona da ugupe men eya anup mek Gegenat taet di, anut koewa tantanewa okom taunek, ae amat tanek Ge gaup gega kakaewa ne guwana kwayup tap, amba ap Ge iwa Gegenat genan ae amat Gega tain.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"2e7629c4-b9e1-4f88-8903-76557948a22c","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"}]},{"phelps":"BH09085","text":"## BOP U’URAEWA\n* Burial\n* Bop U’uraewa ma orup bodu muga aonagaet nani yambun uon tan (15) mugenat den wain amba wa munain.  U’ura ma megenat Bahá’í uruga iyam iyam ta wain.  Ma orup daiton megenat wapi amba uruga ao paina yonain.  At bowarewa gambena eya toenta nain.  (Kitáb-i-Aqdas)\n\n\nMaman!  Ma Ge nao gega apanewa osuwa, Ge anusumat tageni amba Ge pauwa gega den, amba gine namu genan toentanen dim dim uruga imuwarat tan Ge gegenat anusumat taiga.  Ge gegenat ipiri, bagusisi nunan anuianawa.  Irewa yao, Ge Da bigip muga imu warat taianawa amba ta bambam nuga wat wagianawa, Ge gese upuru Gega pae pose gapan dotauvep.  Me yaibobot wandep.  Maman da siya uon, Ge gegenat, koewa imuwarat taiyanawa, wamwam nunianawa puiman mine inap ta, amba piup ge kiman eya venaseni Ge bagusisi gega kanama apa wanden.  Maman ra den siga uon Ge gegenat taedi wamwam koewa nuga Imuwarat taianawa, Uruga Nunianawa. \n\n* Ma den wapen pauwa nani yamben daiton (6) gaun Alláh-u-Abhá wata amba den pauwa (19) mugenat nop ma daiton daiton wa vitait.\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá! \n\n Nu uruga ipiri kaut maman inap enuinit. (19)\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá!\n\nNu uruga ipiri omaninu Maman inap poponagianit. (19)\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá!\n\nNu uruga ipiri bumaganu Maman wanianit.(19)\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá !\n\nNu uruga ipiri wat taragat Maman wat taragasinit. (19)\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá!\n\nNu uruga ipiri gaun Maman inap waiyanit. (19)\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá!\n\nNu uruga ipiri Kwataem momon Maman inap taiyanit. (19)","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"b171204e-5467-4001-a0b4-4de78e221077","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"am","lang_name":"Amharic"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"dgz","lang_name":"Daga"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"Hindi"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"ik","lang_name":"Inupiaq"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"naq","lang_name":"Khoekhoegowab"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"ksd","lang_name":"Kuanua"},{"language":"kgf","lang_name":"Kube"},{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mr","lang_name":"Marathi"},{"language":"med","lang_name":"Melpa"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"meu","lang_name":"Motu"},{"language":"nal","lang_name":"Nalik"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"kj","lang_name":"Oshikwanyama"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"}]},{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"## SOTPELA PREA BILONG KOLI LONG OLGETA WAN WAN DE\n* Short Obligatory Prayer\n\n* Wan wan Bahá’í i ken kolim dispela prea wanpela taim long olgeta wan wan de namel long taim bilong belo stret i go inap long taim bilong san i go daun.  Pastaim em i wasim han na pes, na bihain em i sanap na em i tanim pes bilong em i go long Ples Matmat bilong Bahá’u’lláh long Ples Holi (Israel).  Olsem long Papua Niugini em i sanap na em i lukluk i go long ples we san i go daun na em i tanim i go long raithan liklik, na em i kolim dispela prea.\n\nO God bilong mi.  Mi tokaut nau long Yu Yet i bin wokim mi, bai mi inap long save long Yu na lotuim Yu. Nau tasol mi tokaut olsem, mi no gat strong na Yu strong tru.  Na mi tokaut tu olsem, mi rabis pinis na Yu holim olgeta samting.  \n\nI no gat narapela God.  Yu tasol i stap. Yu Save Helpim Long Taim Bilong Bikpela Trabel.  Yu Inap Long Yu Yet.","name":"Short Obligatory Prayer","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"7eb42b31-b215-4afd-8634-2b4277540f24","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"am","lang_name":"Amharic"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"sne","lang_name":"Bau Bidayuh"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"km","lang_name":"Central Khmer"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"chn","lang_name":"Chinook Jargon"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"cr","lang_name":"Cree"},{"language":"dgz","lang_name":"Daga"},{"language":"dak","lang_name":"Dakota"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"fo","lang_name":"Faroese"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"